entry.string: INSERT INTO employees (first_name, last_name, department, job_title, start_date, employee_type, status, email) VALUES ( #[payload['first_name']] , #[payload['last_name']] , #[payload['department']] , #[payload['job_title']] , #[payload['start_date']] , #[payload['employee_type']] , #[payload['status']] , #[payload['email']] )

UPDATE employees SET first_name= #[payload['first_name']], last_name= #[payload['last_name']], department= #[payload['department']], job_title=#[payload['job_title']], start_date=#[payload['start_date']], employee_type=#[payload['employee_type']], status=#[payload['status']], email=#[payload['email']] WHERE employee_id = #[payload['employee_id']]
